    {
      "id": "65521cad-c851-492d-aefd-ca0ddd7c5c4f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Contribution starts with the introduction of a novel way of representing behavioral features from campus card data. Second, the authors use a multi-head attention mechanism to automatically select the most important high-order combination features. Third, the authors propose a new predictive model that retains accuracy and robustness. ",
